gujarati.context:
Here is the translation:

Fellow fellows' own life, fellow living made it; 
Make short something to be spoken, so listen fellow people.

Here is the translation:

Remained lifeless a mere one, stolen by thieves that one;
Built backwards with tangled hair, two hands, beaten on my seven heads.

Here is the translation:

Then slowly slowly lived, went to one's own village;
Therefore my story is a true tale, I have told my own life.
